<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3993044>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Head in frontal view. (a) Exochus momoii; (b) Exochus nigrifaciatus; (c) Exochus selenanae; (d) Exochus velatus; (e) Exochus ventralis; (f) Exochus vexator; (g) Exochus villosus; (h) Exochus momoii; (i) Exochus nigrifaciatus; (j) Exochus selenanae; (k) Exochus velatus; (l) Exochus ventralis; (m) Exochus vexator; (n) Exochus villosus. Scale bar = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3993044/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3993050>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Morphological characters. (a) Third epipleuron of Exochus nigrifaciatus; (b) third epipleuron of Exochus ventralis; (c) Projection of mesosternum in Exochus dentisternum; (d) Frons of Exochus areolalis; (e) Frons of Exochus alpinus; (f) Frons of Exochus fravomarginatus; (g) Vein Cu-a of Exochus fravomarginatus; (h) Vein Cu-a of Exochus consimilis; (i) Mandible of Exochus adentatus; (j) Mandible of Exochus guttatus; (k) Interantennal process of Exochus mitratus; (l) Interantennal process of Exochus propodealis; (m) Mesoscutum of Exochus depressus; (n) Mesoscutum of Exochus gratus. Scale bars: (a–f), (i–n) = 0.2 mm; (g, h) = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3993050/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3993048>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Propodeum in dorsal view. (a) Exochus argutus; (b) Exochus britannicus; (c) Exochus consimilis; (d) Exochus destitutus; (e) Exochus flavomarginatus; (f) Exochus frontellus; (g) Exochus gratus; (h) Exochus gravipes; (i) Exochus guttatus; (j) Exochus lictor; (k) Exochus lineifrons; (l) Exochus mitratus. Scale bar = 0.2 m m." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3993048/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3993042>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Head in frontal view. (a) Exochus argutus; (b) Exochus britannicus; (c) Exochus consimilis; (d) Exochus destitutus; (e) Exochus flavomarginatus; (f) Exochus frontellus; (g) Exochus gratus; (h) Exochus gravipes; (i) Exochus guttatus; (j) Exochus lictor; (k) Exochus lineifrons; (l) Exochus mitratus. Scale bar = 0.2 m m." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3993042/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3993046>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Propodeum in dorsal view. (a) Exochus acostulatus Lee & Choi, sp. nov.; (b) Exochus adentatus Lee & Choi, sp. nov.; (c) Exochus areolaris Lee & Choi, sp. nov.; (d) Exochus carinalis Lee & Choi, sp. nov.; (e) Exochus dentisternum Lee & Choi, sp. nov.; (f) Exochus depressus Lee & Choi, sp. nov.; (g) Exochus nigritulus Lee & Choi, sp. nov.; (h) Exochus occipitalis Lee & Choi, sp. nov.; (i) Exochus orbitalis Lee & Choi, sp. nov.; (j) Exochus propodealis Lee & Choi, sp. nov.; (k) Exochus alpinus; (l) Exochus antis. Scale bar = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3993046/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

